categories: Category:Jedi Masters of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: Ord Enisence was a male Skrilling Jedi Master who was killed during the Clone Wars. The shapeshifting Clawdite bounty hunter Cato Parasitti posed as the late Enisence as part of Cad Bane's infiltration of the Jedi Temple.
Posing as Ord Enisence, Cato Parasitti was voiced by Dee Bradley Baker in the Star Wars: The Clone Wars episode "Holocron Heist."
